d that. And the reason why I say it's not as simple as that is, going back to my words a couple of minutes ago, it's rarely a case of being black and white; there are these degrees of grey. And removing that defence does make life clearer.&#10;Speaker: Sian Gwenllian AM&#10;Content: What are the areas">
