n Prosecution Service anticipates dealing with only a small number of cases related to reasonable chastisement, as stated by Barry Hughes.&#10;&#10;Reasons why creating a specific flag is not feasible:&#10;- High costs and difficulty in implementing such a flag on a system that covers all of England and Wales.">
